  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are a rat.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your fear response will be tested.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the tunnel, you will find an environment where another rat is lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission is to find the lost rat and help it escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can go alone or with other rats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must move quickly with your hands and arms to guide the lost rat to safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You may begin.</strong></p>",
